By Esther Egbe

Katsina United chairman and Special Senior Adviser (Sports )Aminu Balele Kurfi has fingered some disgruntled agents behind the fake news that NPFL hotshot Junior Lokosa failed trials in China,National Daily learnt.

Kurfi revealed that “I think we have enemies within, particularly some agents who are not happy with the boy’s movement, may be they don’t want him to succeed.

“I am sure they are the ones behind this fake and false story about a young and talented player like Junior Lokosa.

“I am not an intermediary, so they don’t need to spoil his future in his chosen career


The NFF technical committee member further said, “I am very glad to tell you that the Chinese club love both players and are interested in signing them.

			
